                    <span>2014-04-30</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">不错的书，对王韬的历程分析比较细致，是晚清民国史研究的重要参考书。

p51 王韬与洪仁轩的交往。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="232423313">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-232423313" class="vote-count">1</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-232423313" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="232423313">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/neuron/">Rhinover</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
